				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-134166/scp-050#post-2748720</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 17 Feb 2017 01:16:24 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>papachan</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2979740</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I know this might be necroposting but wanted to reply to you anyways in case someone else had the same questions and was looking in the comments for answers.</p> <p>The Customary System Measurement is the measurement system used in the US. So everything in inches, feet, yards, pounds, ounces, quart, etc. Basically, if someone tried to write that SCP-050 weighs about 2.3kg in the record, the record would change to read that SCP-050 weighs about 5lbs (pounds).</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
