				<pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2009 18:55:50 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Melfice</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>278816</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>In other words… the cameras record still the messy office, while it is in actuality cleaned?<br /> Otherwise it can't record nothing out of the ordinary. (And even THAT contradicts itself.)</p> 
				 	]]>
